nd consistent with the topology; end-to-end reachability is verified with normal latency and no loss.\n- No actionable anomalies were detected at this time. Continuous monitoring is advised given the recent BGP session uptimes, but the present state indicates normal operation.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 10131, "output_tokens": 4806, "total_tokens": 14937, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9856}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 3584}}}
